cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.DS

The paper discusses the use of random projections in deep neural networks, which is a topic related to machine learning and artificial intelligence. Based on this, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also involves the use of random projections for dimension reduction, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and data structures (cs.DS).
